window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The Demonic Overlord himself has just dropped the biggest bombshell on Jake, and the stakes have risen again. Now that he’s being pulled deeper into the hierarchy of the Nine Circles, Jake has to find a way to navigate this power-hungry world without the help of his biggest ally—Professor Hightower.</p> <p>The loss couldn’t have come at a worse time. When an ancient demonic sorcerer starts to target Jake, his carefully-constructed world begins to crumble. It’s going to take his entire bonded network of beautiful women, including the ravenous Emma and the feisty Sabrina, to defeat the insidious threat in front of them.</p> <p>Sophomore year is almost over. The real trials are about to begin.</p>"; 
